            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 300,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9333,
            "LocalizeKR": "야경이 너무 아름다워서\n하마터면 목적을\n잊어버릴 뻔했네요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "夜景があまりに美しくて、\n危うく目的を忘れる\nところでした。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 310,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8167,
            "LocalizeKR": "후후,\n작전 중의 방심은\n금물입니다만…",
            "LocalizeJP": "ふふっ、\n作戦中に油断なんて\nダメなのですけど……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 320,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 6500,
            "LocalizeKR": "아, 저… 갑작스럽지만,\n선생님…",
            "LocalizeJP": "……えっと\n……急なのですが、\n先生……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 330,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7200,
            "LocalizeKR": "그러니까… 언제나\n함께해 주셔서\n감사합니다.",
            "LocalizeJP": "その……いつも\n一緒にいてくださって、\nありがとうございます。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 340,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 2400,
            "LocalizeKR": "선생님이 계시지\n않았더라면",
            "LocalizeJP": "先生がいらっしゃら\nなかったら……",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 350,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 6500,
            "LocalizeKR": "저도, RABBIT 소대도\n이만큼 성장하지\n못했을 거예요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "私も、RABBIT小隊も、\nここまで成長でき\nなかったと思います。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 360,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10567,
            "LocalizeKR": "그러니 다음에,\n괜찮으시다면 꼭……",
            "LocalizeJP": "なので今度、\nよろしければ、その――",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 370,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 3000,
            "LocalizeKR": "어라…? 연락이…",
            "LocalizeJP": "……？連絡が……",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 380,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4500,
            "LocalizeKR": "그렇군요…\n앞으로 500m 지점에…",
            "LocalizeJP": "なるほど、\nここから500ｍの地点に……",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 390,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4000,
            "LocalizeKR": "네, 곧 돌입 준비하라는\n연락이네요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "はい。すぐに突入の準備を、\nとのことです。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 400,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8333,
            "LocalizeKR": "선생님, 레펠 링과\n하네스를 착용해주세요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "先生、ラペルリングと\nハーネスを装着してください。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 410,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10500,
            "LocalizeKR": "네? 사용법을\n모르신다고요…?\n그, 그렇군요…",
            "LocalizeJP": "え？使い方が\nわからない……ですか？\nそ、そうでしたか……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_05_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 420,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 6,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7800,
            "LocalizeKR": "괜찮습니다. 그럼\n여기서 기다려 주세요.\n금방 마치고 돌아오겠습니다.",
            "LocalizeJP": "……大丈夫です。\nでは、ここで待っててください。\nすぐに終えて戻ってきます。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle6",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_06_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10038,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003801,
            "DisplayOrder": 430,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 6,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9033,
            "LocalizeKR": "돌아와서 다시\n선생님과 함께, 천천히\n이 야경을 보고 싶어요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "それでまた先生と、\nゆっくりこの夜景が\n見たいので。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
